r6626 | davidl | 2010-08-06 10:35:09 -0400 (Fri, 06 Aug 2010) | 2 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/sim-recon/src/libraries/PID/DPhoton.cc

In seTime method of DPhoton, added code to also set the t0 and t0_err fields of the underlying DKinematicData object. The DPhoton "time" still represents when the particle hit the detector. The t0 represents the time of the photon projected back to the vertex position as determined by the PHOTON_VERTEX_X, ... configuration parameters that by default are set to be at the center of the target (0,0,65). For now, the t0_err is fixed at 2ns, though that will likely need to be changed.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
r6627 | davidl | 2010-08-06 10:37:10 -0400 (Fri, 06 Aug 2010) | 2 lines
