   M /trunk/sim-recon/src/libraries/TRACKING/DHelicalFit.cc

Use sqrt and cbrt instead of pow(x,1./6.).  Tests suggest that the latter is ~50% slower than sqrt(cbrt(x)) on ifarml6. Also implemented slight change to how z-vertex is computed.
